   the successor to Broadcast to the World (2006). The album will be released in
   Japan in July, USA and Europe in August, and released in Canada, South
   America, and Australia shortly afterwards. 'Mental Health' will be the first
   single and the music video will be released a few weeks before the album is
   released.
